<doc id="618943" wikidata="Q5274185" url="?curid=618943" title="Didier Pfirter">
<text>Didier Pfirter (born 1959, in Basel) is a Swiss diplomat.

He was the legal advisor to Álvaro de Soto, the Special Cyprus Advisor of the UN&#x27;s Secretary-General Kofi Annan and Ambassador at Large for Special Assignments at the Swiss Ministry for Foreign Affairs.

Pfirter was appointed Swiss ambassador to Colombia in 2008.

